
login Page :
1. Username field on header menu : //input[@name='username' and @placeholder='Username']
2. Password field on header menu : //input[@name='password' and @placeholder='Password']
3. Sign in button : //button[@class='btn btn-primary btn-sm']
4. Username filed on register form : //input[@id="username-register"]
5. Email filed on register form : //input[@id='email-register']
6. Password filed on register form : //input[@id='password-register']
7. 'Sign up for OurApp' button " : //button[@type='submit']

Main page:
1. Create Post button : //a[@class='btn btn-sm btn-success mr-2']
2. My Profile button : //img[@data-original-title='My Profile']
3. Sign Out button : //button[@class='btn btn-sm btn-secondary']

Post page :
1. Title filed : //input[@id='post-title']
2. Body content filed : //textarea[@id='post-body']
3. Save New Post / Save Updates button : //button[@class='btn btn-primary']
4. Validation success message : //div[@class='alert alert-success text-center']
5. Validation message 'Post successfully updated.': //div[contains(text(),'Post successfully updated.')]
6. Validation message 'Post successfully updated.': //div[contains(text(),'Post successfully deleted')]
7. Edit button : //a[@class='text-primary mr-2']
8. Delete button : //button[@class='delete-post-button text-danger']
9. Post title : //div[@class='d-flex justify-content-between']
10. Body content : //div[@class='body-content'][2]//p[1]
11. Back to post permalink : //a[text()='Â« Back to post permalink']

Profile page :
1. First element in Posts table : //div[@class='list-group']//a[1]

